summary: AN ORDINANCE transferring partial jurisdiction over certain City (Department of Parks and Recreation) property in the Southeast 1/4 of the Northeast 1/4 of Section 22, township 25 North, Range 3 East, W.M., Pleasant Valley Garden Tracts (Magnolia Playground), Magnolia View Addition, Division No. 2 to the City of Seattle, and Dewey's Addition to the City of Seattle (Magnolia Boulevard and park) to the Engineering Department to permit construction and maintenance of a storm drain system with appurtenances.
